title: Whirlpool Appliances, Shimmering Swimming Pool, Beautiful Landscaping
posting_body: ['Located in the heart of Canyon Country near Santa Clarita, Diamond Park Apartments brings you incredible amenities and comfort in a beautiful and convenient Southern California location.', 'With several airy floor plans to choose from, top-of-the-line kitchen designs, private balconies and patios, and easy access to the best of Santa Clarita and Canyon Country, our one and two bedroom apartments for rent offer exquisite living at an affordable price.', 'At Diamond Park in Canyon Country, just minutes from the heart of Santa Clarita, CA we have apartments to meet all your needs for both space and style.', 'APARTMENT FEATURES', '-Pre-Wired For Telephone and Cable', '-Double Stainless Steel Sinks', '-Vertical Blinds', '-Large Private Balcony/Patio', '-Walk-in Closets', '-Washer/Dryer in Each Apartment Home', '-Custom Oak Cabinets', '-Central Air Conditioning', '-Whirlpool Appliances', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', '-On-site Maintenance', '-Gated Access', '-Barbecue and Picnic Areas with Tables', '-Unassigned Open Parking', '-Carport Available', '-Easy Access to Freeways & Shopping', '-Lounging and Sunbathing Areas', '-Soothing Whirlpool Spa/Hot Tub', '-Beautiful Landscaping', '-Two', 'Playgrounds', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'WEBSITE', '<URL>', 'ADDRESS', '27940 Solamint Rd., Canyon Country, CA 91387', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
